HAPPY BIRTHDAY to my forever lifeline, my therapist on speed dial, my drama partner, my soulmate in sister form — my KAVYA DIDI ! 😍😘❤️
Can we just take a moment to appreciate the universe’s planning skills? Like seriously, what are the odds of being born on the same day, exactly 4 years apart?! 
Birthday twins for life, Didi 👯‍♀️!

This year hits different ’cause I’m stepping into my 30s (yes, thirrtttyyy!!) and I couldn’t be more grateful to do it with YOU by my side. You’ve been my guiding light, my biggest hypewoman, and the one who knows I’m losing it before I do. 🤪
So here’s to more shared cakes, shared tears, shared clothes and shared birthdays for a lifetime.

Love you more than my watch collection— and you know that’s saying something! 😉🫶🏻

❤️💜
